de.stock.level

Class LevelPackHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.stock.level.LevelPackHandler

  • public class LevelPackHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    The level pack handler holds all level packs in their specific level stage (See LevelPack and Settings_Level)
    and is the single point of contact for the ActionObserver if a level pack of a level stage
    is needed through the method chooseLevelPack(Integer)
    Author:
    chlange
